reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This set comes with so much stuff! It is all super cute and aesthetically pleasing. It all matches the froggy theme. It comes with so many little fun things. It makes for the perfect gift, stationary gifts are perfect for journaling or scrapbooking. Our daughter loved every single piece of it. She was astonished by the amount of stuff it comes with and they all seem to be very well made and very durable. The pens are easy to write with and they don’t smudge either. Makes for a great fun and unique gift. Also comes with metal pens that you can attach to your lanyard or to your backpack. The pouch is soft and super cute fun frog shape, it fits the pencils and pens perfectly.
